      "item": "init_agents_md",
      "reviewed": true,
      "intent": "If AGENTS.md does not exist, create it with a heading and the agent block. If it exists but does not contain '## 立意', append the block. If '## 立意' is present and force is false, return AlreadyExists. If force is true, append regardless.",
