    {
      "item": "init_sidecar",
      "reviewed": false,
      "intent": "Create a .liyi.jsonc sidecar next to the source file. When discover is true and the language is tree-sitter-supported, pre-populate specs with discovered items including _hints (_has_doc, _body_lines, _likely_trivial based on trivial_threshold). When discover is false, emit empty specs. If the sidecar exists and force is false, return AlreadyExists. Sidecar file name must be <source_filename>.liyi.jsonc.",
